1
00:00:00,093 --> 00:00:03,642
A hurricane hit and devastated
my hometown of Homestead, Florida.

2
00:00:03,794 --> 00:00:04,717
There's a storm coming.

3
00:00:04,768 --> 00:00:05,752
Our people will be fine.

4
00:00:05,843 --> 00:00:07,861
It's the rest of the town
you should be concerned with.

5
00:00:09,500 --> 00:00:11,087
I know a lot more
than you think I do.

6
00:00:11,210 --> 00:00:13,267
There is blood
on the wall of that cell.

7
00:00:13,269 --> 00:00:14,705
I want to know
how he got out.

8
00:00:15,852 --> 00:00:17,498
I would wait for you
forever.

9
00:00:18,204 --> 00:00:20,915
- What's going on?
- It looks like you're having a litter.

10
00:00:21,976 --> 00:00:23,421
- Russell!
- You one of 'em?

11
00:00:23,500 --> 00:00:25,422
- What's goin' on here, Frank?
- Go ahead and look!

12
00:00:26,590 --> 00:00:27,453
But I don't want to leave.

13
00:00:27,453 --> 00:00:30,257
This man may be coming
after our family.

14
00:00:30,727 --> 00:00:31,802
Where's he hiding them?

15
00:00:31,817 --> 00:00:33,772
You and your family-
all dead.

16
00:00:36,947 --> 00:00:38,662
We're not goin' with you.
We're goin' back.

17
00:00:38,668 --> 00:00:39,893
What are we supposed
to tell the kids?

18
00:00:39,896 --> 00:00:42,142
Tell 'em we love 'em.
That's why we're doing this.

19
00:00:42,766 --> 00:00:44,422
Let me out, now!

